<h1>ROLE & RESPONSIBILITIES</h1>

<p>As the Systems & Automation Architect, you will be responsible for:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Systems Architecture:</strong> Design, build, and maintain the technical infrastructure that powers our marketing operations</li>

<li><strong>Marketing Automation:</strong> Develop and optimize automation workflows in GoHighLevel (GHL) and other platforms to streamline client onboarding, lead nurturing, and campaign management</li>

<li><strong>Integration Management:</strong> Build and maintain integrations between various platforms (CRM, email marketing, advertising platforms, analytics tools)</li>

<li><strong>Process Optimization:</strong> Identify bottlenecks and inefficiencies in current systems and implement solutions to improve operational efficiency</li>

<li><strong>Client Support Infrastructure:</strong> Establish and manage the technical support systems for client inquiries and issues</li>

<li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Create and maintain technical documentation for all systems, processes, and workflows</li>

<li><strong>Security & Compliance:</strong> Ensure all systems meet security best practices and data protection requirements</li>

<li><strong>Scalability Planning:</strong> Build systems with scalability in mind to support business growth</li>
</ul>

